thread.title: Kelsey

author: Kelsey
title: Kelsey
text: I don't have much bad to say, but I don't have much good either. My furniture came as expected. The delivery was quick and that was nice, but the delivery people just dropped it off and asked for signatures, they didn't let me check out the furniture and only were at my house for what felt like two seconds. I understand fast is nice, but not always the best option. My furniture is nice, but again I was hoping for a bit more. I should have looked at it more in store. Not disappointed, just not overly excited.
